{"tid":88824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倉務員教女友屈人強姦","createTime":"2017-01-21T01:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T02:40:09.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce108c749fedf9340a2e385e9e351470e548770","tid":88824,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:22:24.000Z","msg":"本報訊】年僅24歲、正辦離婚的倉務員得悉14歲女友與在夜店飲酒結識的男子發生一夜情後，教唆女友誣告對方強姦，女友終向警方和盤托出。有毒癮的倉務員早前認罪，昨求情指希望判監，因恐防一旦判入戒毒所，刑滿獲釋後年僅兩歲8個月的兒子會認不出他。惟裁判官最終決定判他入戒毒所，又勉勵他盡快戒除毒癮，便可照顧兒子，「你個仔應該去公園玩，唔係去戒毒所探你」。<br />\n《戒毒所條例》規定，若法庭判某被告入戒毒所，他入戒毒所的期限不得少於兩個月，但亦不得超過12個月。即使某被告從戒毒所獲釋，懲教署亦可對他頒佈為期一年的監管令。<br />\n<br />\n被告李煒洛早前在屯門法院承認妨礙司法公正罪。辯方指李願意入戒毒所，亦願意承擔責任，但希望被判監。署任主任裁判官周燕珠指李有毒癮，上一次戒毒後需接受監管令，但在監管令後重蹈覆轍，最終判他入戒毒所。<br />\n案情指李的女友於去年7月15日搭上姓蘇男子，跟他返家度春宵。被告着女友誣告蘇強姦，更於同月27日至30日反覆以WhatsApp教她如何報假案，包括要鎮定、有決心、扮說真話及「幻想真係俾人強姦過」，女友向警方錄口供時說出真相。"},{"pid":"814f8e8f403ac4ea4987af8c5d3c2be98128e4ab","tid":88824,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:26:09.000Z","msg":"咁呢2個仆街衰11唔洗判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97799800f097b0d414e778266c9262ebb29d0968","tid":88824,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:29:27.000Z","msg":"兩隻狗公一隻雞"},{"pid":"c61574cbd226c12e0fbfe1ca22d1aadd79222a76","tid":88824,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:32:07.000Z","msg":"14歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088beb311a677a9018e5b8c7084ff842cd4d80ea","tid":88824,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:32:15.000Z","msg":"教人屈強姦呢啲死全家都唔夠"},{"pid":"d6cff5710b4736e76c2ebe5f581ca2aa1fb7f99e","tid":88824,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"衰十一都夠做條友啦，洗唔洗屈老強？"},{"pid":"22b54804038d65e02a26318a72f3e869b1666d23","tid":88824,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:37:58.000Z","msg":"自己都有份衰十一啦"},{"pid":"8b46b7aad31bcf17bed6ec8c0efa788911535217","tid":88824,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"自己衰11仲敢玩法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6364015d5ddea3e64ad3859949f8fc0fced264","tid":88824,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1973ab014849d9c09af2760977913bcd443781bf","tid":88824,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"一年後又繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f2c3f8bd0df80b3e1f93fe072766ba0e5a5c37","tid":88824,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"14歲女友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c51dd0308248a43335cf50a4e25cbd51036d1ae","tid":88824,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T02:21:05.000Z","msg":"咁條女呢? 唔使拉?"},{"pid":"6dc14b76fcd5342990dc4225b58e0774daa5f597","tid":88824,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T02:23:44.000Z","msg":"14歲女友唔告強姦都衰十一啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3741e146eb8db79cfaa978b07179b9bf148005f","tid":88824,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"22歲生仔,24歲就離婚同衰十一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}